CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, pg. 3 reads: "Cute 'Honeybunnies' Paraded... and captured the hears of everyone at the fashion show at A. Leo Weil School. Wearing perky spring outfits with sparkling smiles on their faces, some came out in pairs, as a single, or in one instance, as a trio. "
TitMainTitle: Portrait of two girls, and boy modeling patterned suit, striped bow tie, and hat, standing on stage in A. Leo Weil school for Easter fashion show
